title: TKO Interlude
lyrics:
I'm not available right now so please leave a message and I'll return your call as soon as possible
Hey beautiful, it's me
Just returning your call
You're probably on the plane right now
I know we've both been hella busy lately so

Gonna be good to spend some time

We need it

Can't wait to see you

Have a safe flight

Make sure you hit me when you touch down

You know I'm waitin' for you
